  <constraints>
    <constraint source="ADR-002">Thin Dataverse plugins. MUST NOT register plugins on `sprk_gate_approval` (e.g., do NOT auto-flip status via plugin — the BFF resolver layer handles state transitions).</constraint>
    <constraint source="ADR-017">Run record status (in `sprk_actionrun`, not this entity) follows ADR-017. This gate entity has its own 4-state status: `Pending | Approved | Rejected | TimedOut`. The two state machines are linked but separate.</constraint>
    <constraint source="ADR-019">If any custom API is registered against this entity (deferred to Phase 3), error responses use ProblemDetails RFC 7807.</constraint>
    <constraint source="project">Five gate types fixed per spec scope section: `EthicsCritical`, `MeaningCritical`, `FinalDelivery`, `EngagementAcceptance`, `TeamSelection`, plus `Custom`. No new gate types without spec amendment.</constraint>
    <constraint source="project">Default timeout 5 min per FR-17. `timeoutAt = requestedAt + 5min` if not overridden via `gateConfigJson.timeoutOverride`.</constraint>
    <constraint source="project">Tenant-scoped via required `tenantId` text field (NFR-05). Cross-tenant queries forbidden.</constraint>
    <constraint source="project">Packed into the same solution as tasks 010 + 011 entities for atomic deploy.</constraint>
  </constraints>

